high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the shower, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the green candle off of the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn left and take a step forward, turn left again to face the counter.
Open the second lower drawer from the right below the counter and put the candle inside, then close the drawer.
Turn right and walk up to the shower, then turn left and walk over to the toilet.
Pick up the closest green candle off of the toilet tank.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn right and take a step forward, turn right again to face the counter.
Open the second lower drawer from the right below the counter and put the candle inside, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two green candles into a drawer.

high_descs: turn right and walk over to the right side of the bathroom sink cabinet on your left
grab the candle off of the counter top there
turn around to back up a bit and face the bathroom sink cabinet again
place the candle inside of the bottom pullout drawer underneath the bathroom sink
turn right and move forwards just a tiny bit, and then turn left to face the toilet
grab a candle off of the top of the back side of the toilet there
turn left and move forwards a tiny bit and then turn right to face the right side of the cabinets again
place the candle in the same pullout drawer underneath the bathroom sink again
anns.task_desc: place two candles into a drawer underneath the bathroom sink

high_descs: Turn right, move past the sink, turn left to face the candle on the counter.
Pick up the candle on the counter.
Bring the candle to the drawer under the sink.
Put the candle in the back of the drawer under the sink.
Move to the toilet on the left.
Pick up the front candle on the toilet tank lid.
Bring the candle to the drawer under the sink.
Put the candle in the back of the drawer under the sink, right of the other candle.
anns.task_desc: Put two candles in the drawer under the sink.
